                            Everyone Wears a Mask
                        </div>
                    

                    
                        <div id="breadcrumbs">
                            <a href="/foundation-tales">Tales Hub</a> &raquo; <a href="/series-archive">Series Archive</a> &raquo; <a href="/the-hanged-king-s-comedy">The Hanged King's Comedy</a> &raquo; Everyone Wears a Mask
